'''Imad H. Latheef''' ([[Dhivehi]]: ޢިމާދު ލަޠީފް ) ('''b.''' [[October 27]], [[1966]]), is a Maldivian journalist, columnist and a commentator. He was the foreign news editor, in ''[[Haveeru Daily]]'' news paper in Maldives.
